snippet.title: PLAY DESYNC [PAX WEST SEATTLE, WA - SEP 2-5]
snippet.description:
Footage from a sizzle reel for the Adult Swim Games booth at Pax West 2016.

DESYNC is currently in the BETA stage of development. Content shown here is still being developed and doesn't depict the final quality of the finished game.
